Package: clinicaltrials.gov
Title: ClinicalTrials.gov API v2 Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the ClinicalTrials.gov API v2.
    Search studies, fetch individual study details, outcome measures, adverse
    events, and database statistics. All functions return tibbles with typed
    columns. Handles pagination transparently.
